divs: sighting detailsi had just gotten home from work about 8:15pm, gotten out of my car to walk across the parking lot. i was looking north when i saw an object with many lights in the sky and seem to strobe about every 20 seconds or so. to me the object had a main cylinder body and two v shaped wings with white lights running along the sides of the v's and possibly on the main body as well. it would pulsate\strobe as well. i don't recall hearing anything but traffic noise from the road nearby. the object flew over a apartment complex just north of where i live and the area is well light. it is not a usual flight path for planes to come into the airport. i actually thought it was a plane with landing lights on but after looking at it again i noticed all the lights. i could not make out any color on the object-it was a black silhouette. the object flew west\northwest over the trees and pulsated one last time before i lost sight of it. i just felt curiosity of what i was seeing at the time.
